Description:
Libraries for executing federated programs and computations.

Local Modifications:

- fcp/confidentialcompute/cose.cc
  fcp/confidentialcompute/cose_test.cc

  These files wire up //components/cbor (which Chromium uses) instead of
  libcppbor.

- fcp/confidentialcompute/crypto_test_util.cc

  A utility file useful for testing.  Abseil checks used in this file conflict
  with Chromium, so an implementation using Chromium's checks is provided.
  This can be removed in case we stop using it in Chromium, or upstream switches
  to absl_check.
